Class OccupancyTypeVariant

  • java.lang.Object
    • sensitivity_input.Variant
      • sensitivity_input.OccupancyTypeVariant

  • public class OccupancyTypeVariant
extends Variant
    This class represents a separate occupancy variant, but concerning the structure of the different variants it should be a ScheduleTypeVariant with occupancy as the ScheduleQuantity (with an empty unit) field resp.

    Frank Noack
